 20, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: I saw 'Uqbah ibn Abi Mu\u2019ayt coming to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, while he was praying. 'Uqbah put his sheet around the Prophet\u2019s neck and squeezed it tightly. Abu Bakr came and pulled 'Uqbah away from the Prophet and he said, \"Do\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6819,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/21\/umar-competes-with-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":19771,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Competition: Umar tries to compete with Abu Bakr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, ordered us to give charity and at the time I had some wealth. I said to myself, \u201cToday I will outdo Abu Bakr, if ever there were a day to outdo him.\u201d I went with half\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41197,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/19\/umar-on-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":19771,"position":2},"title":"Umar on Abu Bakr: He was our master, the best of us","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 19, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \"Abu Bakr was the most beloved of us to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, as he was the best of us and our master.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 7407 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33438,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/12\/umar-convinces-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":19771,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Mushaf: Umar convinces Abu Bakr to collect the Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 12, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Zayd ibn Thabit reported: Abu Bak sent for me after the people of Al-Yamamah were killed and Umar ibn al-Khattab was with him. Abu Bakr, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cUmar came to me and said that many reciters of the Quran were killed in the fighting at\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33693,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/09\/fadl-abu-bakr-umar-ammar\/","url_meta":{"origin":19771,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sahaba: Virtues of Abu Bakr, Umar, \u2018Ammar, and Ibn Mas\u2019ud","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 9, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFollow these two men from my companions after me, Abu Bakr and Umar. Accept the guidance of \u2018Ammar, and take the advice of Ibn Mas\u2019ud.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3805 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33256,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/19\/abu-bakr-first-compile-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":19771,"position":5},"title":"Ali on Quran: Abu Bakr first to compile Quran into one book","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Abdu Khayr reported: Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cMay Allah have mercy on Abu Bakr. He was the first to compile the Quran between two covers.\u201d Source: Mus\u0323annaf Ibn Abi\u0304 Shaybah 30229 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ibn Battal \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u062e\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/19771","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuami